1
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,719
General Xie.

2
00:00:42,759 --> 00:00:44,020
Do you want to live?

3
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:45,100
I...

4
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:46,960
can't die.

5
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,219
Your life

6
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,280
is mine.

7
00:01:06,379 --> 00:01:07,480
Xie Lingfeng.

8
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:08,980
You are incompetent.

9
00:01:09,379 --> 00:01:11,260
Don't go back and disgrace the Xie family.

10
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,060
I'll send you off.

11
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:14,859
You should just die

12
00:01:14,859 --> 00:01:15,780
in this defeat.

13
00:01:25,659 --> 00:01:27,500
Thank you for saving my life.

14
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,760
You're thanking the wrong person.

15
00:01:33,739 --> 00:01:34,379
Because

16
00:01:35,579 --> 00:01:37,540
I'm not a good person.

17
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,200
Have you heard of silk thread?

18
00:01:49,599 --> 00:01:50,879
Every full moon,

19
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,319
if not treated with my antidote,

20
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,200
it will act up,

21
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:59,040
You'll feel like

22
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,680
burning in hell.

23
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,659
Do you know

24
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:07,299
what it will turn you into?

25
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,360
It will take away your feelings,

26
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,360
your memories,

27
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,039
and your identity.

28
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,400
By then,

29
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,159
you'll be

30
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,039
the most obedient

31
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:25,979
dog.

32
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,500
[Have you heard of painting the skin and bones?]

33
00:03:00,879 --> 00:03:02,219
[From now on,]

34
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,340
[you]

35
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:07,400
[are the soul tied to my bell.]

36
00:03:09,219 --> 00:03:10,219
[I am the master.]

37
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:12,979
[You are the slave.]

38
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,099
[Your fate is decided by me,]

39
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,520
[not by heaven.]

40
00:03:35,259 --> 00:03:37,120
[This woman saved me from danger,]

41
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,780
[yet she pushed me into the abyss.]

42
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,539
No matter who you are,

43
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:47,879
I will end all of this.

44
00:04:13,139 --> 00:04:14,060
You want to kill me?

45
00:04:14,780 --> 00:04:16,100
I don't have time to play

46
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,220
these tricks with you.

47
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:26,720
No one can be my

48
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,339
master.

49
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,019
My Lord,

50
00:05:32,379 --> 00:05:33,240
your wound is not healed.

51
00:05:33,819 --> 00:05:34,819
It's cold here.

52
00:05:34,939 --> 00:05:36,300
Why don't you find a place to rest?

53
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:38,459
We cannot delay the Queen Mother's order.

54
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,160
Go,

55
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:45,160
is the master painter living here?

56
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:46,899
We are the Xie's Army from the capital,

57
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:48,060
here to visit.

58
00:05:58,939 --> 00:06:00,019
Half a month ago,

59
00:06:00,339 --> 00:06:02,220
the Queen Mother received a painting.

60
00:06:02,939 --> 00:06:05,339
Did you paint it?

61
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,199
Yes, it's my painting.

62
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:15,439
We are here by the Queen Mother's order

63
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,079
to invite talented painters

64
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:18,879
to work in the Imperial Treasure House.

65
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:20,300
Imperial Treasure House?

66
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,839
The place that collects

67
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:23,240
rare treasures for the royal family?

68
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,759
What can a painter like me

69
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:26,319
possibly contribute?
Talented painters

70
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,040
are treasures in themselves.

71
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,079
Since you're a treasure,

72
00:06:32,139 --> 00:06:34,420
joining the house is like joining the collection.

73
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,759
Are you saying

74
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,680
you'll lock me up

75
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,639
as a treasure?

76
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,500
Thank you, General.

77
00:06:54,579 --> 00:06:56,259
Wanna live?

78
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,560
You'll be

79
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,439
the most obedient

80
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:04,420
dog.

81
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:09,439
Buwangtian...

82
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,000
You're alive.

83
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,579
Please behave yourself, General.

84
00:07:31,579 --> 00:07:33,139
I don't believe there are two people

85
00:07:33,139 --> 00:07:34,819
who look exactly the same in this world.

86
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,860
What are you up to?

87
00:07:37,339 --> 00:07:38,379
You've gone from a strange doctor

88
00:07:38,379 --> 00:07:39,860
to the Queen Mother's side.

89
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:41,899
I've always been a painter.

90
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:44,019
When did I become a strange doctor?

91
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:45,779
I don't understand

92
00:07:45,779 --> 00:07:46,860
what you're talking about.

93
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,500
Really?

94
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,480
Let go of me.

95
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:57,139
Let go of me.

96
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,139
You did a clean job.

97
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,579
Looks like you're quite skilled.

98
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:04,040
Your pulse is so erratic.

99
00:08:04,819 --> 00:08:05,379
It seems your body

100
00:08:05,379 --> 00:08:06,500
is already in a dire state.

101
00:08:08,259 --> 00:08:09,439
Isn't all of this

102
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,639
your doing?

103
00:08:11,899 --> 00:08:13,259
Give me the antidote,

104
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,379
Or I don't mind

105
00:08:15,379 --> 00:08:16,699
killing you again.

106
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,420
There are many famous doctors in the capital,

107
00:08:19,259 --> 00:08:20,699
but none of them can cure you.

108
00:08:22,139 --> 00:08:23,259
How could I have the antidote?

109
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,800
I have the means

110
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,860
to tear off your mask.

111
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,399
Last chance.

112
00:08:51,299 --> 00:08:51,980
Xie Mo,

113
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,340
keep an eye on her.
Yes.

114
00:09:00,139 --> 00:09:01,700
That was too close.

115
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,820
Xie Lingfeng almost took action.

116
00:09:04,539 --> 00:09:06,220
My Lady,

117
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:09,700
you're walking a fine line.

118
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:11,139
Are you afraid?

119
00:09:13,779 --> 00:09:14,700
My Lady said

120
00:09:15,419 --> 00:09:17,419
Xie Lingfeng is a lone wolf.

121
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,940
If we don't push him hard,

122
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:22,980
he won't remember the way home.

123
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:25,620
But he's General Xie.

124
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:27,179
the Queen Mother's order.

125
00:09:27,820 --> 00:09:28,980
If we trick him like this,

126
00:09:29,379 --> 00:09:29,860
what if...

127
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:31,139
There's no what if.

128
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,200
We saved him

129
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,200
from the battlefield,

130
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,039
let him

131
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:38,039
kill his master once,

132
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,120
and then

133
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,399
let him see An Rao.

134
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:43,100
Every step he took

135
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,379
was a path laid out by his master.

136
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:46,899
Now,

137
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:49,340
the pawn has crossed the river.

138
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,700
Let's go, Madam.

139
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:53,679
The show has just begun.
Good.

140
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,440
You're just

141
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:00,940
so persistent.

142
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,399
Didn't expect this, did you?

143
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,639
Your master

144
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,559
is very lucky.

145
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:20,000
You crazy dog!

146
00:10:26,899 --> 00:10:27,779
Xie Lingfeng,

147
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,240
I chose the right dog.

148
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,600
You called me a dog,

149
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:38,960
then you are a mad master

150
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,679
who even dares to bite a dog.

151
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,320
You are so sharp.

152
00:10:43,139 --> 00:10:44,779
If you dare to kill your master again,

153
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,720
I will make you

154
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,360
the most obedient snow corpse

155
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:56,759
and let you kneel here forever.
